" <div class=\"graphic\">",
"  <div class=\"figure\" style=\"width: 524px\">",
"   <div class=\"ttl\">",
"    Classic Z-plasty",
"   </div>",
"   <div class=\"cntnt\" style=\"width: 504px; height: 418px; background-image: url(data:image/jpeg;base64,);\">",
"   </div>",
"   <div class=\"lgnd\">",
"    The classic Z-plasty consists of three limbs of equal length. The angles between the central limb and each lateral limb are equal and measure 60&deg;.",
"    <div class=\"footnotes\">",
"    </div>",
